title: The Kari Lake Juggernaut with Kari Lake and Mollie Hemingway
itunes:title: The Kari Lake Juggernaut with Kari Lake and Mollie Hemingway
description:
It's two weeks until election day and Arizona's Kari Lake doesn't just look strong, she looks unstoppable. Lake joins Charlie to talk about why her Trump-style campaign has been such a success, and why Democrat Katie Hobbs has flopped so badly. Then, Mollie Hemingway comes on to explain what shenanigans Democrats might attempt to salvage their failing midterm prospects.
